type.name: ValueGenerated
type.summary: Indicates when a value for a property will be generated by the database. Even when a property is set to be generated by the database, EF may still attempt to save a specific value (rather than having one generated by the database) when an entity is added and a value is assigned, or the property is marked as modified for an existing entity.
